#: ../../user/configuration.md:1
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "設定"

#: ../../user/configuration.md:3
msgid ""
"`@nagatatz/rescript-vitest` is a thin binding layer with no settings of "
"its own. Configuration happens in two places: the ReScript compiler and "
"Vitest."
msgstr ""
"`@nagatatz/rescript-vitest` は薄いバインディング層で、独自の設定はありません。設定は ReScript コンパイラと "
"Vitest の 2 か所で行います。"

